.shop domain FAQ

What is .shop domain?

A .shop domain is a top-level domain (TLD) ideal for eCommerce sites and online retailers. It's a signal to customers that your website is a place to buy products or services, enhancing your brand's visibility and relevance in the digital marketplace.

What is a .store domain?

A .store domain is another TLD similar to .shop, designed specifically for businesses that sell goods or services online. It serves as an immediate indicator that your website is an eCommerce platform.

What is the difference between .shop and .store domains?

Both domains are tailored for eCommerce but may convey slightly different connotations. The .shop domain suggests a broader range of shopping experiences, while .store might imply a more traditional retail environment. Be mindful of your location; “Shop” is more commonly used in the UK whereas “Store” is more commonly used in the US.

Is .shop domain good for SEO?

Yes, a .shop domain can be beneficial for SEO as it clearly signifies the commercial intent of your website, which can help in ranking for shopping-related search queries.

Is .shop a good extension?

The .shop extension is an excellent choice for businesses focused on selling products or services online. It's short, memorable and directly associated with shopping.

What is the benefit of a .shop domain?

A .shop domain immediately identifies your site as an eCommerce platform, which can help attract customers looking to make purchases online and can enhance your brand's digital presence.

Is .com or .shop better?

Choosing between a .com or a .shop depends on your business needs. While .com is more generic and widely recognized, a .shop may provide clearer branding for an eCommerce business.

Can I get a .shop domain for free?

Wix offers a free domain voucher with select plans, allowing you to register a new .shop domain at no cost for the first year. Check out available domain options at Wix to see if you qualify.

Can I keep my contact information hidden when I register?

Yes, you have the option of selecting “Private Registration” when registering a domain with Wix. This privacy protection service will keep your contact information confidential on WHOIS.

Is it easy to renew my domain?

Wix makes it simple to renew your domain with automatic renewal options ensuring your online presence remains uninterrupted. You can extend your domain registration by adding up to 3 additional years to your subscription.

Transferring an existing domain to Wix is straightforward. Follow these steps to initiate the transfer process and manage all of your web assets in one place.
